Package es.upm.ies.goniophotometer.threads

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalibrationThread
    This thread does the automatic calibration while the main thread maintains the GUI functionality active in case the user wants to stop the calibration.
    MeasureThread
    This thread does the automatic measure while the main thread maintains the GUI functionality active in case the user wants to stop the measure.
